                    <p>When you fly, you may experience unpleasant, overcrowding, poor food, and almost no legroom situations that can turn your flight into a nightmare rather than a convenience. The patience of passengers on foreign flights is put to the ultimate test. There are a few high-end airlines that make flying a pleasurable experience.</p>
                            <p>Money may not be able to buy everything, but it can buy a first-class ticket. Hence, we have come up with some of the best airlines you need to check. These airlines can provide a <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/major-airlines.aspx">luxury flight</a> for you. Your breath will be taken away by their brilliance, cleanliness, hygiene, and comfort. You will never have a more luxurious or comfortable travel experience than what they offer. On that topic, let me welcome you to the top ten most opulent airlines in the world. </p>


                    <h2>Etihad Airways</h2>

                    <p>Etihad Airways has ranked number one in several lists and won nearly every travel award imaginable. They have incredibly lavish premium flights available. Passengers on Etihad can get everything they want on a plane. Would you like to spend your journey in a two-bedroom suite? That's exactly what Etihad's "The only Residence'' provides, plus you'll get a personal chef. It's as if you're staying in a five-star hotel at an altitude of 35,000 feet (10,668 meters). </p>

                    <h2>Emirates Airline</h2>

                    <p>Emirates Airline is known for its lavish travel and its first-class rooms are no exception. The experience resembles a high-end hotel suite in the sky. To start your gastronomic journey, sample some of the high-quality, one-of-a-kind foods and drinks that are available. You can order everything you want at any time and have it delivered to your suite. You'll be treated like royalty by one of the world's most prestigious luxury airlines. Put on your noise-canceling headphones and lose yourself in the entertainment hidden behind the floor-to-ceiling sliding doors. Lastly, turn off the lights and retire to bed to prepare for the upcoming time. </p>

                    <h2>Lufthansa Airline</h2>

                    <p>To begin with the best about this airline, you hire a limousine service to take you to the airport, and while you wait for your journey, you can dodge the throng by waiting in an exclusive lounge. The first-class cabin crew devotes their full attention to you onboard. Whether you want to sleep, rest or work, the timelessly elegant design is complemented with excellent materials that appeal to all demands. Michelin-star cuisine is also available, which can be paired with award-winning wines. You can choose to watch the latest movies, listen to music, play games, or engage in other forms of entertainment. Lastly, don't be scared to request that your seat be converted into a nice bed by the personnel. </p>

                    <h2>Air France, Air Carrier</h2>

                    <p>Air France's "La Première" provides first-class passengers with luxury from the moment they book. As soon as you step into one of the first-class suites, you'll be treated like royalty. Have a nice snack, a full dinner, or a drink in the lounge. The cabin staff is ready to deliver outstanding table service, with a wide selection of wines and Alain Ducasse gourmet meals. The smooth leather, suede, delicate wood, and metallic accents will certainly catch your eye. You'll be entranced for hours with over 650 hours of on-demand entertainment on a touchscreen device and a comfortable seat. When you need to sleep, simply convert your seat into a bed with a memory foam mattress, a pillow, and a luxury duvet. </p>

                    <h2>Delta Airlines</h2>

                    <p>Delta One® has a dedicated in-cabin flight attendant and beautiful amenities that make a meaningful difference in how you spend your time flying. On long-haul international flights and in a few long-haul domestic markets, the Delta One experience is available. A 180-degree flat-bed seat, a specialized flight attendant, and a variety of additional amenities will ensure a pleasurable voyage. In the cabin, enjoy reinvented dining with seasonal selections, the freshest regionally sourced ingredients, and chef-curated dishes. <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/delta-airlines-cheapest-tickets.aspx">Delta Airlines</a> collaborates with chefs from all around the world, and you reap the benefits. </p>


                    <h2>American Airlines</h2>

                    <p>American Airlines' flagship first-class offers you a home-like experience by providing you with slippers, pajamas, pillows, mattress pads, and blankets. You will get 5-star services here. Grab your devices and enjoy Wi-Fi throughout the journey. Additionally, take advantage of free entertainment such as TV shows, free movies, music, games, and more. You can also enjoy multi-course meals along with an amazing collection of wines. They have partnered with the James Beard Foundation so that they can offer you exclusive dishes which are designed by their elite chefs. </p>

                    <h2>Southwest Airlines</h2>

                    <p>Southwest is the major airline in the US. Priority boarding is guaranteed for passengers, which is ideal for open-seating plans because people can board the plane first, choose their seats, and settle down before the rest of the passengers. Check-in is also expedited, with all security and check-in lines being streamlined. Business passengers will also receive a complimentary premium drink voucher that can be used on the day of travel and includes alcoholic beverage options. </p>

                    <h2>Qatar Airways</h2>

                    <p>Qatar Airways is a well-known airline with fantastic short and long-haul flights. The wide cabins of Qatar Airways provide complete seclusion and exceptional comfort. Your seat transforms into a super-comfy, totally flatbed that will make you forget you're thousands of feet in the air. With inbuilt Wi-Fi, USB ports, and laptop power connectors, you can turn any place into a terrific work environment. You can then enjoy delectable cuisine produced by some of the world's most talented chefs, some of whom have worked at Michelin-starred hotels. The à la carte menu, which is available on-demand, includes a variety of foods to suit everyone's tastes. </p>

                    <h2>British Airways</h2>

                    <p>British Airways, the UK's foremost luxury airline, offers luxurious first-class private rooms to its guests. In your first-class suites, enjoy on-demand entertainment with noise-canceling headphones. Use the free Wi-Fi and charging outlets to get some work done. You can visit the first-class lounge in between flights for some scrumptious treats from the à la carte menu, which features British classics. In addition to fine dining cuisine, the UK's best luxury airline serves snacks and beverages. Allow the staff to convert your seat into a flatbed with microfiber mattress and 400-thread-count linens after everything is done. </p>

                    <h2>Cathay Pacific Airways</h2>

                    <p>One of the most costly airlines in the world is Cathay Pacific Airways. A <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/flights/flights-from-hong-kong-to-usa.aspx">round-trip flight</a> from Hong Kong to New York will set you back at around $26,572. You will have an incredible time with huge cabin space for this pricing. You may nap in a comfortable bed while watching your favorite movie or series on your flat screen. Also, while you're passing the time on your travels, don't forget to enjoy your gourmet meals and a large range of international wines. </p>

